N%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/Kim-l%C5%A9-y/poem-c5IV0WUJ3OQZnkcLrRf3VQ">Kim lũ y - 金縷衣</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Thu-N%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/author-QADl9-7RmBPrvunDgmvbgw">Đỗ Thu Nương</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ti%E1%BA%BFt-Hu%E1%BB%87/L%C5%A9ng-%C4%90%E1%BA%A7u-ng%C3%A2m/poem-DcrNd3xJDkMcaL1Tx2C6sQ">Lũng Đầu ngâm - 隴頭吟</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ti%E1%BA%BFt-Hu%E1%BB%87/author-PjzIG1r2C2XpMeVwfYjbJw">Tiết Huệ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Khu%E1%BA%A5t-Nguy%C3%AAn/Ly-tao/poem-lRoe60dlSbBq5oc1ZRJWhQ">Ly tao - 離騷</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Khu%E1%BA%A5t-Nguy%C3%AAn/author-2RPFDWkSQLaYkT3rYIGIrQ">Khuất Nguyên</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%E1%BA%A1-Tr%C4%83n/T%C3%A1i-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-kh%C3%BAc-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem--FK5OdCjDBas-dsirOWlew">Tái thượng khúc kỳ 1 - 塞上曲其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%E1%BA%A1-Tr%C4%83n/author-1SPKfkHlUAnw6r-glqobvQ">Tạ Trăn</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Khuy%E1%BA%BFt-danh-Trung-Qu%E1%BB%91c/Ti%C3%AAu-Tr%E1%BB%8Dng-Khanh-th%C3%AA-%C4%90%E1%BB%87-t%E1%BB%A9-%C4%91o%E1%BA%A1n/poem-pie5Fia6OX3GJydppNrLBw">Tiêu Trọng Khanh thê - Đệ tứ đoạn - 焦仲卿妻－第四段</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Khuy%E1%BA%BFt-danh-Trung-Qu%E1%BB%91c/author-7Jx-9zMDy2CyYi7fIk3zRA">Khuyết danh Trung Quốc</a>)<br></div>	</div>
